        "category": "ancestry",
        "description": {
            "value": "<p>You appear not as an android, but a traditional organic creature. You become trained in Deception and gain a +2 circumstance bonus to checks to @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.actions.Item.Impersonate] living creatures as your biotech changes your body's shape or texture as part of the disguise. Creatures recognize you as a @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.heritages.Item.Biotech Android] only if they succeed at a @Check[perception|defense:deception] check against your Deception DC, and you don't have to attempt a Deception check to interact with someone to conceal the fact that you're a biotech android; a check happens only if someone else tries to uncover your heritage.</p>"
